WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:02.753
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.753 --> 00:05.336
I WANNA BE WITH YOU.
I WANT US TO HAVE THAT CHANCE.

00:05.336 --> 00:07.218
IT'S SPREAD.
STAGE IV LYMPHOMA.

00:07.218 --> 00:09.430
HOW LONG? HOW M--
HOW MANY YEARS?

00:09.430 --> 00:11.222
NOT YEARS. MONTHS.

00:11.222 --> 00:13.554
WHERE'S VICTORIA?
 I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING.

00:13.554 --> 00:15.226
AND I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

00:15.226 --> 00:16.847
I KNOW HOW VICTORIA
PULLED THIS OFF.

00:16.847 --> 00:18.059
AAH! UHH!

00:18.059 --> 00:20.271
SHE MADE IT LOOK LIKE I ATTACKED
HER IN A PARKING GARAGE.

00:20.271 --> 00:23.694
SHE STAGED HER PENTHOUSE
TO LOOK LIKE SHE WAS ASSAULTED,

00:23.694 --> 00:25.816
MAKING THE WORLD BELIEVE
THAT I WAS A MONSTER

00:25.816 --> 00:27.488
WHO BURNED THE QUEEN ALIVE.

00:27.488 --> 00:28.989
WE HAVE DENTAL RECORDS
AND X-RAYS.

00:28.989 --> 00:32.243
SHE SWITCHED THEM WITH A WOMAN
NAMED MARY GAINES.

00:32.243 --> 00:33.654
Louise: I FOUND THE HOODIE
THAT VICTORIA SAID

00:33.654 --> 00:35.706
EMILY WAS WEARING
WHEN SHE ATTACKED HER.

00:35.706 --> 00:37.538
YOU TOLD
DETECTIVE HUNTER THIS?

00:37.538 --> 00:39.120
I NEED TO RETAIN YOUR SERVICES
IMMEDIATELY.

00:40.461 --> 00:41.752
YOU ARE ALIVE.

00:41.752 --> 00:43.214
[ SQUISH ]
 [ GASPS ]

00:43.214 --> 00:45.045
SHH.

00:46.046 --> 00:48.429
[ BIRDS CALLING ]

00:48.429 --> 00:50.471
Emily: WHEN I WAS
A LITTLE GIRL,

00:50.471 --> 00:52.593
THE DELINEATION
BETWEEN GOOD AND EVIL

00:52.593 --> 00:55.806
WAS AS CLEAR
AS NIGHT AND DAY.

00:55.806 --> 00:57.438
BUT AS LIFE GROWS COMPLICATED,

00:57.438 --> 00:59.770
THAT LINE BLURS, AND WE LEARN
TO JUSTIFY OUR ACTIONS

00:59.770 --> 01:03.774
WHEN WE BELIEVE
WE'VE CROSSED IT.

01:03.774 --> 01:05.946
IF WE AREN'T CAREFUL,

01:05.946 --> 01:08.109
THOSE CHOICES CAN FILL US
WITH DARKNESS,

01:08.109 --> 01:10.991
LEAVING US DESTINED
TO NEVER SEE LIGHT AGAIN.

01:10.991 --> 01:13.114
YOU'RE GETTING PRETTY GOOD
AT THAT.

01:14.325 --> 01:15.536
[ LAUGHS ]

01:22.203 --> 01:24.125
[ PLANE APPROACHING OVERHEAD ]

01:24.125 --> 01:26.757
WHAT'S WRONG, SWEETHEART?

01:26.757 --> 01:29.710
WHY ARE THERE BAD PEOPLE,
DADDY?

01:29.710 --> 01:31.592
IS THIS ABOUT THE CRASH
YOU SAW ON THE TV?

01:31.592 --> 01:33.013
THE FLIGHT 197?

01:36.137 --> 01:38.599
I DON'T THINK
THAT PEOPLE ARE BORN BAD.

01:38.599 --> 01:41.142
I THINK IT'S THEIR CHOICES
THAT MAKE THEM WHO THEY ARE.

01:41.142 --> 01:44.725
I THINK SOMETIMES
PEOPLE CONVINCE THEMSELVES

01:44.725 --> 01:47.188
THAT DOING SOMETHING BAD
IS OKAY.

01:47.188 --> 01:49.029
WHAT IF I DO THAT?

01:49.029 --> 01:50.110
YOU WOULD NEVER.

01:50.110 --> 01:52.403
YOU ALWAYS LISTEN
TO YOUR HEART.

01:52.403 --> 01:54.155
AND IF YOU EVER GO
OFF THE PATH,

01:54.155 --> 01:55.616
DAD'S GONNA BE THERE
TO BRING YOU BACK.

01:55.616 --> 01:56.867
PROMISE.

02:00.201 --> 02:01.041
[ BUZZER SOUNDS ]

02:01.041 --> 02:02.703
[ METAL DOOR SLIDES CLOSED ]

02:04.044 --> 02:05.166
DETECTIVE?

02:05.166 --> 02:08.127
DO YOU KNOW WHEN BEN HUNTER'S
COMING IN THIS MORNING?

02:08.127 --> 02:09.590
HE'S NOT.

02:09.590 --> 02:12.173
OKAY, WELL, THIS AFTERNOON --
 DETECTIVE HUNTER IS DEAD.

02:12.173 --> 02:16.217
[ Whispers ] WHAT?

02:16.217 --> 02:18.309
NO.

02:18.309 --> 02:20.060
NO, I CAN'T BELIEVE THAT.

02:20.060 --> 02:22.183
IF YOU HAD ANYTHING
TO DO WITH THIS,

02:22.183 --> 02:23.224
I'M GONNA FIND OUT.

02:25.226 --> 02:29.480
[ METAL DOOR SLIDES
OPEN AND CLOSED ]

02:29.480 --> 02:31.362
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

02:42.203 --> 02:45.085
[ SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE ]
 DID ANYONE RECOGNIZE YOU?

02:45.085 --> 02:48.209
NOBODY BATTED AN EYE.

02:48.209 --> 02:50.050
AND WHY WOULD THEY?

02:50.050 --> 02:52.132
VICTORIA GRAYSON'S DEAD.

02:52.132 --> 02:55.135
I'M SO GLAD YOU'RE SAFE.

02:56.427 --> 02:58.008
THANKS TO YOU.

02:58.008 --> 03:00.931
I TOLD HER TO GET YOU OUT
OF THERE BEFORE BEN FOUND YOU.

03:00.931 --> 03:03.183
I NEVER EXPECTED HER TO --

03:03.183 --> 03:04.565
I KNOW THAT.
 [ SIGHS ]

03:04.565 --> 03:06.567
WHAT THAT WOMAN DID TO BEN
WAS HORRIFIC.

03:06.567 --> 03:09.570
NOW ALL WE CAN HOPE IS THAT
NO MORE BLOOD WILL BE SHED.

03:09.570 --> 03:12.273
[ Whispers ] RIGHT?

03:12.273 --> 03:14.815
UM...

03:14.815 --> 03:17.238
I'VE ARRANGED IT SO THAT
YOU CAN STAY HIDDEN HERE

03:17.238 --> 03:19.029
IN OUR NEW HEADQUARTERS
UNTIL TOMORROW,

03:19.029 --> 03:22.453
WHEN YOU'LL BOARD A PRIVATE JET
TO MONTPELLIER.

03:26.997 --> 03:28.038
THIS ALL STARTED

03:28.038 --> 03:31.292
WHEN AMANDA CLARKE CHANGED
HER IDENTITY.

03:31.292 --> 03:34.174
AND NOW IT ENDS
WITH ME CHANGING MINE.

03:34.174 --> 03:37.258
DID YOU SPEAK TO CHARLOTTE
AND PATRICK?

03:37.258 --> 03:39.179
THEY'VE BEEN INVITED
TO THE FUNERAL.

03:41.181 --> 03:43.143
VICTORIA...

03:43.143 --> 03:44.845
YOU KNOW, UNTIL EMILY
IS CONVICTED

03:44.845 --> 03:48.269
AND YOU'RE SAFELY ABROAD,
YOU CANNOT CONTACT THEM.

03:48.269 --> 03:51.111
WELL...

03:51.111 --> 03:53.113
IT WOULDN'T MAKE
ANY DIFFERENCE.

03:54.855 --> 03:59.199
I WROTE AND PHONED CHARLOTTE
SO MANY TIMES.

03:59.199 --> 04:02.493
BUT I NEVER GOT A RESPONSE.

04:02.493 --> 04:04.705
YOU KNOW BETTER THAN ANYONE
HOW COMPLICATED

04:04.705 --> 04:07.578
THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN
A MOTHER AND A DAUGHTER CAN BE.

04:07.578 --> 04:11.211
EVEN MORE THAN YOU REALIZE.

04:11.211 --> 04:13.674
THE CORPSE I PASSED OFF
AS MY OWN

04:13.674 --> 04:15.716
WAS MY MOTHER.

04:17.878 --> 04:19.930
Man: ALL RISE.

04:19.930 --> 04:22.091
COURT IS NOW IN SESSION.

04:22.091 --> 04:25.936
THE HONORABLE JUDGE JESSE MOSS
PRESIDING.

04:25.936 --> 04:27.227
Moss: PLEASE BE SEATED.

04:29.059 --> 04:30.481
[ Lowered voice ] AMANDA,

04:30.481 --> 04:32.893
ARE YOU ABSOLUTELY SURE
ABOUT THIS?

04:32.893 --> 04:34.395
[ Whispers ] I'M POSITIVE.

04:34.395 --> 04:35.986
Moss: I SEE BOTH COUNSEL
ARE PRESENT.

04:35.986 --> 04:39.159
LET'S GET STARTED, SHALL WE?

04:39.159 --> 04:40.571
YOUR HONOR,
ON BEHALF OF MY CLIENT,

04:40.571 --> 04:43.113
I'D LIKE TO THANK YOU
FOR AGREEING TO THIS HEARING.

04:43.113 --> 04:45.746
THIS HAD BETTER BE WARRANTED,
MS. CLARKE.

04:45.746 --> 04:47.207
IT IS, YOUR HONOR.

04:47.207 --> 04:50.040
WELL, ENLIGHTEN US THEN,
WOULD YOU?

04:50.040 --> 04:52.873
MY FATHER ONCE SAID
THAT NO ONE IS BORN BAD,

04:52.873 --> 04:58.088
THAT...IT'S OUR CHOICES
THAT DEFINE WHO WE ARE.

04:58.088 --> 04:59.590
BY THOSE STANDARDS,

04:59.590 --> 05:03.804
BOTH MYSELF AND VICTORIA GRAYSON
ARE FAR FROM SAINTS.

05:03.804 --> 05:06.016
BUT ONLY ONE OF US
CROSSED A LINE... [ SIGHS ]

05:06.016 --> 05:07.307
THAT WE CAN'T COME BACK FROM.

05:07.307 --> 05:09.640
YOUR HONOR, SHE'S MAKING
UNFOUNDED CLAIMS

05:09.640 --> 05:12.893
ABOUT THE VICTIM'S CHARACTER
BEFORE THE TRIAL'S EVEN BEGUN.

05:12.893 --> 05:15.436
GET TO THE POINT, MS. CLARKE.

05:15.436 --> 05:17.988
I REQUESTED TO COME BEFORE
THE COURT TODAY

05:17.988 --> 05:20.741
BECAUSE THERE IS SOMETHING
YOU NEED TO KNOW.

05:23.153 --> 05:27.207
I AM GUILTY OF THE MURDER
OF VICTORIA GRAYSON.

05:27.207 --> 05:28.208
[ GALLERY SHOUTING AT ONCE ]

05:41.301 --> 05:43.133
WHAT ON EARTH ARE YOU DOING?
WHY DID YOU PLEAD GUILTY?

05:43.133 --> 05:44.465
BEN IS DEAD.

05:44.465 --> 05:46.056
WHAT?

05:46.056 --> 05:49.179
HE WAS KILLED LAST NIGHT,
IN HIS HOME.

05:49.179 --> 05:50.310
THEY'RE SAYING IT WAS
AN ACCIDENT,

05:50.310 --> 05:51.852
BUT I DON'T BELIEVE THAT.

05:51.852 --> 05:55.145
HE WAS MURDERED,

05:55.145 --> 05:56.106
AND IT'S MY FAULT.

05:56.106 --> 05:57.778
SO YOU ADMIT
TO KILLING VICTORIA?

05:57.778 --> 05:59.069
THAT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

05:59.069 --> 06:02.032
I DID IT, DAD.
 YOU'RE LYING.

06:02.032 --> 06:04.034
YOU WOULD NEVER KILL ANYONE.
THAT'S NOT WHO YOU ARE.

06:07.197 --> 06:08.409
I DON'T CARE
IF THEY'RE LISTENING.

06:08.409 --> 06:11.752
I LOST 20 YEARS OF MY LIFE
FOR SOMETHING I DIDN'T DO.

06:11.752 --> 06:13.584
YOU CAN'T GIVE UP NOW.

06:13.584 --> 06:15.706
I DON'T WANNA SPEND WHAT'S LEFT
OF MY LIFE WITHOUT YOU.

06:15.706 --> 06:16.997
THAT'S IT, CLARKE. TIME'S UP.

06:16.997 --> 06:18.589
CAN YOU JUST GIVE US
FIVE MORE MINUTES, PLEASE?

06:18.589 --> 06:19.880
I LOVE YOU.

06:19.880 --> 06:22.092
AMANDA. AMANDA!

06:23.424 --> 06:24.635
[ SLAMS RECEIVER ]

06:24.635 --> 06:26.717
EMILY'S A GENIUS.
 HOW IS PLEADING GUILTY

06:26.717 --> 06:28.469
TO A MURDER YOU DIDN'T COMMIT
SMART?

06:28.469 --> 06:31.221
OH, AFTER MY INCARCERATION,

06:31.221 --> 06:34.645
I DECIDED THAT WE NEEDED
A PLAN IN PLACE IF...

06:34.645 --> 06:35.896
WELL, MORE LIKELY "WHEN,"

06:35.896 --> 06:37.898
ONE OF US ENDED UP
GETTING ARRESTED AGAIN.

06:37.898 --> 06:40.821
SO I BONED UP ON ALL THE SPECS
AND SECURITY

06:40.821 --> 06:44.735
FOR EVERY HOOSEGOW
IN A 200-MILE RADIUS.

06:44.735 --> 06:46.657
SO...EMILY PLED GUILTY
SO SHE COULD BE MOVED

06:46.657 --> 06:48.529
INTO A MAXIMUM SECURITY PRISON?

06:48.529 --> 06:50.951
WHERE WE'RE GONNA
MOVE HER OUT.

06:50.951 --> 06:54.084
YOUR MOTHER DID UNSPEAKABLE
THINGS TO YOU, VICTORIA.

06:54.084 --> 06:56.537
I THOUGHT YOU'D BANISHED HER
FROM YOUR LIFE.

06:56.537 --> 06:59.089
I DID.

06:59.089 --> 07:00.501
AND IN THE EIGHT YEARS SINCE,

07:00.501 --> 07:02.713
I'VE TRIED NEVER TO GIVE HER
A SECOND THOUGHT.

07:02.713 --> 07:06.096
BUT THE NIGHT AFTER
AMANDA DESTROYED ME,

07:06.096 --> 07:08.218
I RECEIVED AN UNEXPECTED CALL.

07:08.218 --> 07:11.101
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:11.101 --> 07:12.933
[ Weak and raspy voice ]
VICTORIA.

07:12.933 --> 07:14.685
I DIDN'T EXPECT YOU'D SHOW.

07:14.685 --> 07:17.187
[ WHEEZES, EXHALES SHARPLY ]

07:17.187 --> 07:18.148
[ COUGHS ]

07:18.148 --> 07:20.020
WELL, IF I HADN'T,

07:20.020 --> 07:22.022
YOU'D HAVE THOUGHT YOURSELF
THE BIGGER PERSON.

07:22.022 --> 07:23.984
WELL, COULDN'T HAVE THAT,
COULD WE?

07:23.984 --> 07:26.196
I KNOW YOU THINK

07:26.196 --> 07:28.028
I WAS A HORRIBLE MOTHER.

07:28.028 --> 07:30.240
[ BREATHING UNEVENLY ]

07:30.240 --> 07:33.664
AND THAT AFTER YOU...
HUMILIATED ME

07:33.664 --> 07:36.336
THAT THANKSGIVING,

07:36.336 --> 07:38.539
I BET YOU HOPED I'D...

07:38.539 --> 07:39.840
[ Whispers ] CURL UP AND DIE.

07:41.001 --> 07:43.173
I LOVED YOU, MOTHER...

07:44.214 --> 07:48.088
SO MUCH THAT I TOOK THE FALL FOR
THE MURDER THAT YOU COMMITTED,

07:48.088 --> 07:51.221
HOPING THAT ONE DAY
YOU WOULD LOVE ME BACK.

07:51.221 --> 07:55.015
AND INSTEAD, WHEN I WAS
RELEASED TO YOU,

07:55.015 --> 07:58.599
I FOUND THAT LECHEROUS MAN
IN OUR HOME,

07:58.599 --> 08:00.060
WAITING FOR ME.

08:00.060 --> 08:03.564
I DIDN'T ASK YOU HERE
TO FIGHT.

08:03.564 --> 08:07.107
I CHANGED MY NAME SO...

08:07.107 --> 08:10.320
THERE'D BE NO CHANCE
YOU COULD HURT ME AGAIN.

08:10.320 --> 08:11.872
[ EXHALES ]

08:11.872 --> 08:14.705
AND IMAGINE MY SURPRISE
WHEN I...

08:14.705 --> 08:18.418
I SAW ON TELEVISION
THAT GIRL

08:18.418 --> 08:21.041
THAT YOU FORCED TO DO
THE SAME THING.

08:21.041 --> 08:26.837
I HEARD ABOUT
DANIEL'S PASSING,

08:26.837 --> 08:28.508
THAT CHARLOTTE IS
IN REHAB...

08:28.508 --> 08:30.220
[ COUGHS ] AGAIN.

08:30.220 --> 08:32.222
[ COUGHS ]

08:32.222 --> 08:35.596
I EVEN HEARD ABOUT...

08:35.596 --> 08:37.057
YOUR BASTARD...

08:38.729 --> 08:40.851
WHO ABANDONED YOU

08:40.851 --> 08:43.063
JUST LIKE
YOU ABANDONED HIM.

08:44.855 --> 08:48.198
SO NOW YOU TELL ME, VICTORIA.
 [ Whispers ] NO.

08:48.198 --> 08:51.151
WHO WAS THE BETTER MOTHER?

08:51.151 --> 08:54.454
I MUST'VE INHERITED MY HEART
FROM MY FATHER.

08:56.496 --> 08:59.459
YOU OWE ME THE TRUTH.
WHO WAS HE?

08:59.459 --> 09:03.253
DIDN'T YOU RECOGNIZE HIM,
VICTORIA?

09:05.716 --> 09:08.759
THAT LECHEROUS MAN

09:08.759 --> 09:13.553
THAT YOU SEDUCED
INTO YOUR BED... [ COUGHS ]

09:13.553 --> 09:17.848
[ BREATHING SHALLOWLY ]

09:17.848 --> 09:20.230
[ CRYING ]

09:20.230 --> 09:22.352
YOU...

09:22.352 --> 09:24.645
YOU ARE
A CRUEL, LOATHSOME BITCH

09:24.645 --> 09:26.566
WHO DESERVES TO BURN IN HELL.

09:26.566 --> 09:29.359
WELL, THEN...

09:29.359 --> 09:33.403
WE'LL CONTINUE
THIS CONVERSATION...

09:33.403 --> 09:34.955
THERE.

09:34.955 --> 09:38.118
[ MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY ]

09:38.118 --> 09:42.202
[ FLATLINING ]

09:46.336 --> 09:48.629
Victoria:
IT WAS ONLY IN DEATH

09:48.629 --> 09:50.170
THAT MY MOTHER COULD FINALLY DO
SOMETHING GOOD

09:50.170 --> 09:52.132
FOR HER DAUGHTER.

10:00.020 --> 10:03.603
[ LOUD EXPLOSION ]

10:03.603 --> 10:05.896
YOU'RE THE ONLY FAMILY
I HAVE LEFT,

10:05.896 --> 10:07.357
THANKS TO AMANDA.

10:07.357 --> 10:08.939
I'M HERE FOR YOU.

10:08.939 --> 10:11.732
BUT SHE IS STILL A THREAT.

10:11.732 --> 10:15.155
THE ONLY REASON
FOR HER TO CONFESS

10:15.155 --> 10:17.157
IS THAT
SHE'S UP TO SOMETHING.

10:17.157 --> 10:19.409
WELL,
WHATEVER HER NEXT MOVE,

10:19.409 --> 10:21.081
I WILL GO TO MY GRAVE

10:21.081 --> 10:23.453
BEFORE I ALLOW HER
TO HURT MY CHILDREN AGAIN.

10:34.424 --> 10:36.807
[ FOOTSTEPS DEPART ]

10:36.807 --> 10:39.850
[ TICKING ]

10:39.850 --> 10:44.564
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

10:44.564 --> 10:46.356
[ CHAIR WHEELS ROLL ]

10:58.118 --> 11:01.661
[ CONTINUES TICKING ]

11:01.661 --> 11:05.455
[ ALARM BLARING ]
 [ INMATES SCREAMING ]

11:05.455 --> 11:07.167
MASCELLI, WHERE'S THE FIRE?

11:07.167 --> 11:08.458
IT COULD BE ANYWHERE!

11:08.458 --> 11:11.842
OPEN 'EM UP! ALL OF 'EM!
DO IT!

11:11.842 --> 11:14.344
[ MEN SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY,
DOOR CLOSES ]

11:14.344 --> 11:16.136
[ CELL DOORS UNLOCKING ]

11:16.136 --> 11:20.180
[ ALARM CONTINUES BLARING ]

11:20.180 --> 11:23.183
[ INMATES SHOUTING AT ONCE ]

11:25.976 --> 11:29.359
[ SHOUTING CONTINUES,
GATE UNLOCKS ]

11:35.986 --> 11:38.989
[ KEYS JANGLE, MAN SPEAKING
INDISTINCTLY OVER P.A. ]

11:38.989 --> 11:41.992
[ ALARM CONTINUES BLARING ]

11:52.883 --> 11:54.885
YOU KNOW...

11:54.885 --> 11:57.547
A MOST DISTINCT SENSATION
OF DéJà VU.

11:57.547 --> 11:58.799
JUST SAYIN'.

11:58.799 --> 12:01.141
[ EXHALES ]
THANKS FOR BEING HERE.

12:01.141 --> 12:02.843
WOULDN'T BE ANYWHERE ELSE.

12:02.843 --> 12:04.394
WELL, AFTER THE NUMBER I DID
ON THEIR SECURITY SYSTEM,

12:04.394 --> 12:06.516
WE SHOULD HAVE PLENTY OF TIME.

12:06.516 --> 12:08.018
WHAT'S OUR NEXT MOVE?

12:08.018 --> 12:10.150
A SPOT JUST OPENED UP
AT BEDFORD HILLS CORRECTIONAL.

12:10.150 --> 12:13.113
I'M GONNA FIND VICTORIA
AND PUT HER IN IT.

12:17.447 --> 12:18.819
Man: [ Amplified voice ]
ANYONE WHO BELIEVES

12:18.819 --> 12:20.861
WILL NOT COME UNDER JUDGMENT,

12:20.861 --> 12:24.204
BUT HAS PASSED FROM DEATH
TO LIFE.

12:24.204 --> 12:27.167
THE HOUR'S COMING
WHEN THE DEAD WILL HEAR

12:27.167 --> 12:29.209
THE VOICE OF THE SON OF GOD

12:29.209 --> 12:30.330
AND ALL WHO HEAR...

12:30.330 --> 12:33.083
I CAN'T BELIEVE
THEY DIDN'T SHOW.

12:33.083 --> 12:35.715
VICTORIA DESERVED BETTER.
 ...THE GOSPEL OF THE LORD.

12:35.715 --> 12:39.549
Congregants: PRAISE TO YOU,
LORD JESUS CHRIST.

12:39.549 --> 12:41.181
Louise: [ Amplified voice ]
MOST PEOPLE THINK

12:41.181 --> 12:43.143
THEY KNEW WHO
VICTORIA GRAYSON WAS.

12:45.265 --> 12:50.150
THE STRONG
QUEEN OF THE HAMPTONS.

12:50.150 --> 12:52.562
BUT THEY'RE WRONG.

12:52.562 --> 12:55.065
VICTORIA'S TOUGH EXTERIOR

12:55.065 --> 12:57.357
WAS MERELY AN ARMOR

12:57.357 --> 12:59.699
BUILT UP TO PROTECT A HEART

12:59.699 --> 13:03.163
WHOSE CAPACITY TO LOVE

13:03.163 --> 13:05.495
WAS UNMATCHED.

13:05.495 --> 13:07.367
I KNOW THIS...

13:07.367 --> 13:10.790
[ Voice breaking ]
BECAUSE SHE OPENED IT UP TO ME,

13:10.790 --> 13:13.213
EMBRACING ME AS HER OWN.

13:15.715 --> 13:18.418
[ SNIFFLES ]

13:18.418 --> 13:20.180
[ BREATHES UNEVENLY ]

13:20.180 --> 13:22.472
THE LOSS OF VICTORIA GRAYSON

13:22.472 --> 13:24.054
IS A TRAGEDY.

13:24.054 --> 13:28.979
BUT THE REAL TRAGEDY IS THAT
SO FEW

13:28.979 --> 13:32.812
GOT TO EXPERIENCE THE INTENSITY
WITH WHICH SHE LOVED.

13:34.104 --> 13:35.986
I CONSIDER MYSELF BLESSED

13:35.986 --> 13:38.238
HAVING BEEN A RECIPIENT
OF THAT LOVE.

13:38.238 --> 13:42.202
AND I CAN ONLY HOPE
THAT WHILE SHE WAS ALIVE,

13:42.202 --> 13:44.905
SHE FELT I RETURNED IT IN KIND.

13:46.036 --> 13:48.999
THANK YOU.

13:48.999 --> 13:51.041
BEN WOULD'VE COME HERE
FROM THE MORGUE

13:51.041 --> 13:53.163
WHEN HE REALIZED THAT
MARY GAINES' BODY WAS MISSING.

13:53.163 --> 13:55.045
BUT THERE'S NO SIGN
THAT HE WAS HERE.

13:55.045 --> 13:56.716
WELL, MAYBE VICTORIA'S HENCHMAN
KILLED HIM

13:56.716 --> 13:58.798
BEFORE HE HAD A CHANCE.

14:02.012 --> 14:04.424
WHO THE HELL IS MARY GAINES,
ANYWAY?

14:12.472 --> 14:14.184
OH, MY GOD.

14:14.184 --> 14:15.395
WHAT?

14:16.566 --> 14:18.068
IT'S HER MOTHER.

14:18.068 --> 14:21.191
VICTORIA BURNED
HER OWN MOTHER'S CORPSE

14:21.191 --> 14:23.073
IN THE FIRE.

14:23.073 --> 14:24.864
THAT'S INSANE.

14:24.864 --> 14:26.196
[ CELL PHONE RINGS ]
 [ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

14:26.196 --> 14:28.078
[ RING ]

14:28.078 --> 14:29.289
TELL ME YOU HAVE SOMETHING.

14:29.289 --> 14:30.490
WHAT, OTHER THAN

14:30.490 --> 14:32.452
YOUR GREAT ESCAPE TRENDING
ON TWITTER?

14:32.452 --> 14:35.585
I DIDN'T THINK THEY'D ADMIT
TO LOSING ME SO QUICKLY.

14:35.585 --> 14:37.047
WE GOTTA MOVE.

14:37.047 --> 14:39.049
You're not going anywhere,
Miss America's Most Wanted!

14:39.049 --> 14:42.422
Look, I can't get you out
if you get arrested again,

14:42.422 --> 14:44.134
so just sit tight.

14:44.134 --> 14:45.885
I'LL TALK TO YOU LATER.
 [ BEEP ]

14:45.885 --> 14:47.097
WHAT IS IT?

14:47.097 --> 14:49.219
THE FLOOR WAS JUST CLEANED,

14:49.219 --> 14:51.011
BUT ONLY IN THIS AREA.

14:53.103 --> 14:54.854
WHAT'S THAT LOOK LIKE
TO YOU?

14:58.568 --> 15:00.570
[ SIGHS ]

15:02.152 --> 15:04.074
BEN WASN'T KILLED AT HOME.

15:05.865 --> 15:08.078
IT HAPPENED HERE.

15:08.078 --> 15:09.239
[ BELL DINGS ]

15:11.531 --> 15:12.993
[ HORN BLARES IN DISTANCE ]

15:12.993 --> 15:14.794
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

15:14.794 --> 15:17.587
DON'T WORRY. NO ONE SAW ME,
NOT EVEN YOU.

15:17.587 --> 15:19.089
YOU WERE AT
YOUR OWN FUNERAL?

15:19.089 --> 15:21.921
[ SPEAKS FRENCH ]
I'M TRYING TO PROTECT YOU.

15:21.921 --> 15:24.174
WHY MUST YOU INSIST
ON MAKING IT SO DIFFICULT?!

15:24.174 --> 15:25.755
I'M SORRY...
 [ SIGHS ]

15:25.755 --> 15:28.008
BUT I WANTED TO SEE MY CHILDREN
FOR ONE LAST TIME.

15:28.008 --> 15:31.101
BUT APPARENTLY, THEY DIDN'T HAVE
THE SAME DESIRE.

15:31.101 --> 15:32.142
OH, VICTORIA.

15:32.142 --> 15:33.553
LOUISE DID.

15:33.553 --> 15:37.227
I CANNOT ALLOW SOMEONE
WHO CARES ABOUT ME

15:37.227 --> 15:41.561
TO LANGUISH AWAY
IN UNNECESSARY MOURNING.

15:41.561 --> 15:44.654
BRING HER TO ME.
I HAVE TO TELL HER THE TRUTH.

15:44.654 --> 15:47.567
YOU'RE PUTTING OUR LIVES IN
THE HANDS OF AN UNSTABLE WOMAN.

15:47.567 --> 15:49.829
YOU HEARD HER EULOGY.
SHE'S DEVOTED TO ME.

15:49.829 --> 15:52.162
YOUR JOURNEY IS
IN ENOUGH JEOPARDY AS IT IS.

15:52.162 --> 15:54.874
VICTORIA,
EMILY IS COMING FOR US.

15:58.458 --> 16:01.501
WELL, I KNEW
THIS WASN'T OVER.

16:01.501 --> 16:03.633
BUT THERE'S ONE COURSE OF ACTION
WE CAN TAKE.

16:07.587 --> 16:09.049
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ] NO.

16:09.049 --> 16:11.971
NO, IT'S OUT OF THE QUESTION.

16:11.971 --> 16:14.434
I WON'T BE A PART
OF ANY MORE BLOODSHED.

16:14.434 --> 16:17.727
MARGAUX, I NEVER WANTED
AMANDA CLARKE DEAD.

16:17.727 --> 16:19.559
I WANT HER TO BE
IN SOLITARY CONFINEMENT

16:19.559 --> 16:20.810
FOR THE REST OF HER LIFE.

16:20.810 --> 16:24.234
YOUR CONTACT CAN CAPTURE
AND PUT HER THERE.

16:26.606 --> 16:28.948
I SAY WE MAKE A RUN FOR IT.

16:28.948 --> 16:31.111
EVERY SECOND
WE'RE NOT TRACKING VICTORIA,

16:31.111 --> 16:33.413
SHE GETS FURTHER AWAY.

16:33.413 --> 16:35.035
NOLAN SAID TO SIT TIGHT,

16:35.035 --> 16:37.077
SO THAT'S WHAT
WE'RE GONNA DO.

16:37.077 --> 16:38.958
WE NEED TO REST.

16:38.958 --> 16:40.960
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU ACTUALLY SLEPT?

16:40.960 --> 16:43.213
WE'RE NOT SAFE HERE, JACK.
I'M NOT GONNA SLEEP.

16:44.834 --> 16:46.426
[ SIGHS ]

16:48.048 --> 16:50.890
YOU'RE SAFE.

16:50.890 --> 16:52.092
I'M HERE.

16:55.475 --> 16:56.976
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

16:56.976 --> 16:59.519
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

16:59.519 --> 17:00.940
YOU KNOW, WHEN I STARTED
ALL OF THIS,

17:00.940 --> 17:03.733
I DIDN'T KNOW...

17:03.733 --> 17:05.023
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

17:05.023 --> 17:07.567
SOMEONE WAS GONNA FIGURE OUT
WHAT I WAS DOING IF...

17:07.567 --> 17:10.859
IF I WOULD FAIL, IF THE WHOLE
THING WOULD FALL APART.

17:10.859 --> 17:12.742
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

17:14.704 --> 17:18.117
REMEMBER THAT DAY...

17:18.117 --> 17:20.500
I RAN INTO YOU AND SAMMY
IN THE PARK?

17:24.924 --> 17:28.338
SUDDENLY, I FELT LIKE...

17:28.338 --> 17:30.470
EVERYTHING WAS GONNA BE OKAY.

17:34.304 --> 17:37.347
YOU'VE ALWAYS MADE ME
FEEL SAFE, JACK.

17:39.939 --> 17:42.102
I KNOW THINGS...
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

17:42.102 --> 17:45.105
GOT COMPLICATED SINCE THEN
WITH AIDEN AND AMANDA...

17:47.527 --> 17:51.111
BUT I NEVER STOPPED FEELING
THAT WAY WHEN I WAS AROUND YOU.

17:53.573 --> 17:55.575
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

17:55.575 --> 17:59.199
I GUESS I'M JUST SCARED.
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

18:01.701 --> 18:05.084
THIS WHOLE MESS ISN'T OVER YET,
AND I DON'T KNOW

18:05.084 --> 18:07.207
HOW IT'S GONNA END.

18:07.207 --> 18:09.669
NEITHER DO I.

18:11.551 --> 18:14.134
BUT I KNOW

18:14.134 --> 18:15.805
THAT I WON'T LET IT END...

18:18.218 --> 18:19.519
WITHOUT THIS.

19:41.100 --> 19:42.642
THE REMAINS WERE TOO BURNT
FOR D.N.A.,

19:42.642 --> 19:44.514
SO ALL WE HAD TO GO ON
WERE THE TEETH WE RECOVERED.

19:44.514 --> 19:47.016
BUT THE CORONER CHECKED
HER DENTAL RECORDS.

19:47.016 --> 19:48.808
IT'S DEFINITELY
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

19:54.864 --> 19:57.777
YOU KNOW, I DON'T THINK
VICTORIA WOULD'VE APPRECIATED

19:57.777 --> 20:00.320
YOU PULLING ME OUT OF
HER FUNERAL RECEPTION EARLY.

20:00.320 --> 20:03.373
YOU NEED TO STOP BURYING
YOUR FEELINGS, MARGAUX.

20:03.373 --> 20:06.085
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
HOW YOU CAN BE SO COLD.

20:06.085 --> 20:07.877
YOU WILL.

20:07.877 --> 20:09.038
[ BELL DINGS ]

20:10.750 --> 20:12.131
[ GASPS ]

20:12.131 --> 20:14.043
HELLO, POPPET.

20:16.215 --> 20:19.759
LOUISE, YOU ARE A TREASURED PART
OF MY FAMILY.

20:19.759 --> 20:22.552
THEN WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

20:22.552 --> 20:24.264
BECAUSE I COULDN'T RISK
IMPLICATING YOU

20:24.264 --> 20:27.226
IN CASE SOMETHING HAD
GONE AWRY.

20:27.226 --> 20:28.768
AND NOW I REALIZE
THE ERROR OF MY WAYS.

20:28.768 --> 20:30.650
I AM SO SORRY.

20:30.650 --> 20:33.983
I JUST...

20:33.983 --> 20:36.446
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHERE WILL YOU GO?

20:36.446 --> 20:38.858
SOMEPLACE YOU CANNOT COME.

20:38.858 --> 20:43.072
BUT I PROMISE,
WE WILL BE REUNITED ONE DAY.

20:43.072 --> 20:45.034
UNTIL THEN,

20:45.034 --> 20:48.207
I NEED YOU TO KEEP UP
THE CHARADE.

20:48.207 --> 20:49.669
FOR ME.

20:51.170 --> 20:52.332
[ Whispers ] OF COURSE.

20:52.332 --> 20:54.173
[ SNIFFLES ]

20:54.173 --> 20:56.085
MAMA.

20:56.085 --> 20:57.927
OH.

20:59.299 --> 21:01.681
NOW I'VE BEEN LOOKING INTO
MARGAUX'S FINANCES,

21:01.681 --> 21:03.933
AND SHE RECENTLY WIRED
A LOT OF MONEY

21:03.933 --> 21:06.185
INTO SOMEONE'S ENCRYPTED ACCOUNT
IN THE CAYMANS.

21:06.185 --> 21:07.647
MAYBE THAT'S FOR VICTORIA.
IT COULD LEAD US RIGHT TO HER.

21:07.647 --> 21:09.098
I THOUGHT THE SAME THING,

21:09.098 --> 21:10.520
BUT THE ACCOUNT'S BEEN OPEN
FOR YEARS,

21:10.520 --> 21:13.062
RECEIVING LARGE SUMS
FROM ALL OVER THE GLOBE.

21:13.062 --> 21:15.775
I THINK I MAY HAVE FIGURED OUT
WHO IT BELONGS TO.

21:15.775 --> 21:18.608
THE F.B.I. HAVE BEEN TRYING
TO PIN DOWN

21:18.608 --> 21:21.070
A MERCENARY WHO CALLS HERSELF
"WHITE GOLD."

21:21.070 --> 21:24.073
MOST PEOPLE DON'T EVEN BELIEVE
SHE EXISTS, BUT...
 [ BEEP ]

21:24.073 --> 21:25.495
WAIT. HANG ON.
 WHAT IS IT?

21:28.037 --> 21:30.790
DAVID, MARGAUX JUST CUT
THE GHOST ASSASSIN

21:30.790 --> 21:33.913
ANOTHER CHECK.
 [ CELL PHONE RINGS ]

21:33.913 --> 21:35.174
[ CELL PHONE CLICKS ]
 EMS.

21:35.174 --> 21:37.006
I GOT IT, NOLAN.
 WAIT. GOT WHAT, EMS?

21:37.006 --> 21:39.759
EVIDENCE THAT VICTORIA SWITCHED
THE BODIES.
 NO, NO, NO. THAT'S GREAT, BUT --

21:39.759 --> 21:41.130
I FOUND HER MOTHER'S ORIGINAL
DENTAL RECORDS. IT'S ALL HERE.

21:41.130 --> 21:42.342
Emily!

21:42.342 --> 21:44.183
LOOK, YOU'RE IN DANGER, GIRL.

21:44.183 --> 21:46.976
Margaux paid a hit woman
to take out Ben,

21:46.976 --> 21:48.428
AND YOU ARE NEXT.

21:48.428 --> 21:49.729
That's why I told you
to stay at the house.

21:49.729 --> 21:52.101
You're safe there.
 NO, WE'RE NOT.

21:52.101 --> 21:53.393
BEN WAS KILLED THERE.

21:53.393 --> 21:55.435
IF THE ASSASSIN FINDS OUT,
SHE'LL RETRACE HER STEPS.

21:55.435 --> 21:57.937
THEN YOU NEED TO GET AS FAR AWAY
FROM THAT HOUSE AS POSSIBLE.

21:57.937 --> 21:59.068
WELL...
 [ CLOSES DRAWER ]

21:59.068 --> 22:01.070
JACK'S STILL THERE.
I'M NOT JUST GONNA LEAVE HIM.

22:01.070 --> 22:02.281
I'm going back.
 NO, HEY, ALL RIGHT.

22:02.281 --> 22:04.243
YOU KNOW WHAT? EMILY, WE'RE
SENDING THE POLICE RIGHT NOW.

22:04.243 --> 22:05.905
DO NOT GO BACK THERE.

22:05.905 --> 22:09.118
YOU DO, YOU'RE EITHER CAUGHT
OR YOU'RE DEAD.

22:11.290 --> 22:13.913
EMILY?

22:13.913 --> 22:15.044
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

22:15.044 --> 22:16.165
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

22:18.217 --> 22:19.218
EMILY?

22:28.097 --> 22:31.681
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

22:35.435 --> 22:38.237
[ BLADE WHOOSHES ]
 [ GRUNTING ]

22:42.902 --> 22:44.744
[ GRUNTS ]
 [ SQUISH ]

22:44.744 --> 22:46.195
[ GROANS ]
 [ BLADE ZINGS ]

22:46.195 --> 22:49.368
[ GASPING, BREATHING RAGGEDLY ]

22:53.162 --> 22:56.085
[ GROANING ]

22:56.085 --> 22:59.208
EITHER YOU TELL ME
WHERE AMANDA IS AND YOU DIE,

22:59.208 --> 23:01.841
OR YOU DON'T TELL ME
AND YOU DIE SLOWER.

23:01.841 --> 23:04.003
GO TO HELL.

23:04.003 --> 23:05.555
BAD CALL.

23:05.555 --> 23:07.507
[ DOOR BANGS OPEN ]

23:07.507 --> 23:09.429
Man: MOVE, MOVE!

23:09.429 --> 23:10.850
[ MEN SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY ]
 [ GROANS ]

23:12.932 --> 23:14.514
[ GASPING ]

23:14.514 --> 23:16.065
Man: SIR,
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

23:16.065 --> 23:18.317
Man: [ Distorted voice ] WE GOT
A MAN DOWN IN HERE.

23:18.317 --> 23:21.020
SEND 'EM UP ASAP.

23:21.020 --> 23:22.572
HANG IN THERE, SIR.

23:22.572 --> 23:24.193
HELP IS ON ITS WAY.

23:24.193 --> 23:26.616
[ SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE ]
 [ GROANING ]

23:28.488 --> 23:30.239
[ Whispers ] COME ON.

23:30.239 --> 23:33.202
[ MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY ]

23:33.202 --> 23:35.535
Nolan: HANG IN, BUDDY.

23:35.535 --> 23:37.457
SOMETHING WRONG?
 [ CURTAIN RINGS SWOOSH ]

23:37.457 --> 23:39.418
[ Whispers ] EMS!

23:39.418 --> 23:41.340
THIS PLACE IS CRAWLING
WITH COPS.

23:41.340 --> 23:43.042
I DON'T CARE.

23:43.042 --> 23:44.253
BY THE TIME I GOT
TO MARION'S HOUSE,

23:44.253 --> 23:46.926
THEY WERE LOADING HIM IN
THE AMBULANCE. I HAD TO SEE HIM.

23:46.926 --> 23:48.758
[ MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY ]

23:48.758 --> 23:50.139
[ Whispers ] JACK.

23:52.221 --> 23:54.013
[ SNIFFLES ]

23:56.556 --> 23:59.769
[ Whispers ]
PLEASE DON'T LEAVE ME.

23:59.769 --> 24:01.060
[ Voice breaks ] I NEED YOU.

24:06.365 --> 24:10.199
I'M NOT GONNA PUT VICTORIA
IN PRISON.

24:10.199 --> 24:11.781
I'M GONNA PUT HER IN THE GROUND.

24:11.781 --> 24:13.452
AND DON'T YOU DARE TRY
TO STOP ME.

24:13.452 --> 24:14.704
I WON'T.

24:14.704 --> 24:16.075
DO IT.

24:16.075 --> 24:18.247
I'M GONNA TAKE CARE OF THE BITCH
MARGAUX PAID TO DO THIS.

24:18.247 --> 24:19.499
NOLAN, YOU CAN'T.
SHE'S DANGEROUS.

24:19.499 --> 24:21.040
SO AM I.

24:21.040 --> 24:22.632
I TRAINED FOR FOUR YEARS

24:22.632 --> 24:24.924
WITH THE MOST DANGEROUS SENSEI
I KNOW.

24:24.924 --> 24:27.176
I CAN HANDLE HER.

24:27.176 --> 24:28.217
WE STILL HAVE
TO FIND VICTORIA.

24:28.217 --> 24:30.049
WE DON'T KNOW WHERE
SHE'S HIDING.

24:30.049 --> 24:31.430
I DO.

24:40.269 --> 24:41.480
[ SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE ]

24:41.480 --> 24:44.193
[ COMPUTER POWERS ON ]

24:46.105 --> 24:47.947
[ DECANTER CLINKS ]

24:51.070 --> 24:53.412
NO, NO.

24:53.412 --> 24:54.914
NO.

24:54.914 --> 24:57.997
NO, NO.
 [ TAPS KEYS ]

24:57.997 --> 24:59.999
NO, IT'S...

24:59.999 --> 25:01.040
ARRêTEZ!

25:02.542 --> 25:04.383
IT'S NO USE, MARGAUX.

25:04.383 --> 25:06.125
YOU CAN'T ESCAPE THIS.

25:06.125 --> 25:09.088
HOW DID YOU GET IN HERE?
LEAVE NOW.

25:09.088 --> 25:12.051
DOESN'T MATTER
IF YOU ADMIT IT OR NOT.

25:12.051 --> 25:13.633
I HAVE PROOF...
 [ POURS LIQUOR ]

25:13.633 --> 25:16.135
THAT YOU HIRED
THE MERCENARY

25:16.135 --> 25:18.097
THAT MURDERED BEN,

25:18.097 --> 25:19.518
PUT JACK IN THE HOSPITAL.

25:19.518 --> 25:20.770
JACK?

25:20.770 --> 25:23.142
W-WHAT HAPPENED?
IS HE ALL RIGHT?

25:23.142 --> 25:25.695
HE IS IN CRITICAL CONDITION,
THANKS TO YOU.

25:27.146 --> 25:29.148
I NEVER WANTED ANYONE
TO GET HURT.

25:29.148 --> 25:33.112
I WAS ONLY TRYING TO PUT EMILY
BACK BEHIND BARS

25:33.112 --> 25:34.153
WHERE SHE BELONGS.

25:34.153 --> 25:36.155
AND WHERE DO YOU BELONG,
MARGAUX? HMM?

25:37.867 --> 25:40.580
YOU AND EMILY ARE
FAR FROM INNOCENT.

25:40.580 --> 25:42.712
I KNOW THE CRIMES
YOU'VE COMMITTED FOR HER.

25:42.712 --> 25:46.125
CAN'T YOU SEE THAT
YOU AND I ARE THE SAME?

25:46.125 --> 25:47.466
EVERYTHING WE'VE DONE

25:47.466 --> 25:49.128
WAS OUT OF LOYALTY
TO THE PEOPLE WE LOVE.

25:49.128 --> 25:52.011
AND YOU CROSSED A LINE
AND YOU KNOW IT!

25:52.011 --> 25:53.673
YOU TOOK A LIFE!

25:53.673 --> 25:56.015
[ Voice breaking ]
HEY, I'VE LOST PEOPLE, TOO!

25:56.015 --> 25:59.729
MY FATHER! DANIEL!
I LOST MY OWN CHILD!

25:59.729 --> 26:01.891
AND IT DOESN'T MATTER
HOW HARD WE TRY.

26:01.891 --> 26:04.443
WE CAN'T GET THEM BACK.

26:04.443 --> 26:07.526
WE CAN'T UNDO WHAT WE'VE DONE.
[ CRIES ]

26:07.526 --> 26:10.189
SOMEONE ONCE TOLD ME THAT...

26:10.189 --> 26:12.401
IT'S OUR DECISIONS

26:12.401 --> 26:14.403
THAT DEFINE WHO WE ARE.

26:14.403 --> 26:15.865
WELL...

26:18.998 --> 26:21.000
YOU'VE STILL GOT
A DECISION TO MAKE.

26:23.963 --> 26:26.836
[ MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY ]

26:26.836 --> 26:28.087
DAVID?

26:28.087 --> 26:30.129
JACK. OH, THANK GOD.

26:30.129 --> 26:31.801
HOW YOU FEELIN'?

26:31.801 --> 26:33.763
WHERE'S AMANDA?
 NO, NO, NO. HEY.

26:33.763 --> 26:35.094
[ GROANS ]
 EASY.

26:35.094 --> 26:37.596
NOLAN LEFT ME A MESSAGE,
SAID THAT SHE WAS OKAY.

26:37.596 --> 26:39.929
I'LL, UH... [ SIGHS ]

26:39.929 --> 26:41.140
I'LL LET THE DOCTOR KNOW
THAT YOU'RE AWAKE.

26:41.140 --> 26:43.773
SO SHE CAN CHECK YOU OUT.

26:43.773 --> 26:45.064
DAVID?

26:45.064 --> 26:46.896
YEAH?

26:49.188 --> 26:52.942
DO YOU REMEMBER WHEN
AMANDA AND I WERE...

26:52.942 --> 26:53.993
WERE KIDS,
AND SHE MADE US HAVE

26:53.993 --> 26:56.035
THAT LITTLE WEDDING
ON THE BEACH?

26:56.035 --> 26:58.367
WITH THE, UM...

26:58.367 --> 27:00.830
THE PIPE CLEANER RINGS, RIGHT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:00.830 --> 27:03.663
[ CHUCKLES ]
 YEAH.
HOW COULD I FORGET THAT?

27:03.663 --> 27:07.456
YOU APPROVED OF US
BACK THEN.

27:07.456 --> 27:09.128
WOULD YOU STILL APPROVE TODAY?

27:09.128 --> 27:10.800
JACK, YOU HAD A ROUGH DAY.

27:10.800 --> 27:13.422
NO. I'M SERIOUS, DAVID.

27:13.422 --> 27:16.055
WHEN THIS IS ALL OVER,
I WANNA MARRY YOUR DAUGHTER.

27:18.177 --> 27:21.060
BUT I WAS HOPING TO HAVE
YOUR BLESSING.

27:21.060 --> 27:23.182
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:23.182 --> 27:24.724
WELL, UH...

27:24.724 --> 27:26.105
YOU HAVE IT.

27:26.105 --> 27:29.188
I CAN'T IMAGINE LEAVING AMANDA
IN BETTER HANDS THAN YOURS.

27:33.072 --> 27:34.483
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

27:43.913 --> 27:45.494
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

27:45.494 --> 27:48.087
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:48.087 --> 27:49.749
[ HORN BLARES IN DISTANCE ]

27:54.754 --> 27:56.135
LOUISE.

27:56.135 --> 27:58.557
PLEASE STOP.

27:58.557 --> 28:00.599
I AM DONE LISTENING TO YOU.

28:00.599 --> 28:03.222
YOU HAVE BEEN USING ME
THIS WHOLE TIME.

28:03.222 --> 28:05.264
I AM NOTHING BUT A PAWN
TO YOU.

28:05.264 --> 28:07.146
NO, POPPET, I LOVE YOU.

28:08.517 --> 28:10.309
[ Whispers ] I NEVER WANTED
TO HURT YOU.

28:10.309 --> 28:12.361
[ Whispers ] BUT YOU DID.

28:12.361 --> 28:14.023
[ SNIFFLES ]

28:14.023 --> 28:17.196
AND THERE'S SOMEONE ELSE
YOU HURT MUCH MORE.

28:25.284 --> 28:27.086
HELLO, VICTORIA.

28:34.133 --> 28:36.005
MARGAUX: Nolan Ross is
the perfect bait.

28:36.005 --> 28:38.677
Put him in danger,
and Amanda will come.

28:38.677 --> 28:41.300
YOU SHOULD CONSIDER PUTTING ME
ON RETAINER, LADY MARMALADE.

28:41.300 --> 28:44.183
This will be the last time,
I assure you.

28:44.183 --> 28:46.225
THAT'S WHAT THEY ALL SAY.

28:49.438 --> 28:51.270
YOU CLOSED?

28:51.270 --> 28:53.112
BUMMER.

28:53.112 --> 28:55.114
COULD SURE USE A SHOT.

28:55.114 --> 28:57.907
WELL, I CAN MAKE AN EXCEPTION.

28:57.907 --> 28:59.028
WHAT'S YOUR POISON?

28:59.028 --> 29:01.160
BOURBON.

29:01.160 --> 29:03.322
[ LIQUOR POURS ]

29:05.034 --> 29:06.996
AAH!
 NOW...

29:06.996 --> 29:08.327
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]
 WITH YOUR FREE HAND,

29:08.327 --> 29:10.129
YOU'RE GONNA CALL
YOUR BESTIE AMANDA

29:10.129 --> 29:12.832
AND YOU'RE GONNA LET HER KNOW
THAT HER PRESENCE IS REQUIRED.

29:12.832 --> 29:15.795
YOU KNOW THE BEST THING
ABOUT WHITE GOLD?

29:17.877 --> 29:19.258
IT'S AN EXCELLENT CONDUCTOR.

29:19.258 --> 29:20.589
[ ZAPS ]

29:20.589 --> 29:21.931
[ THUD ]
 [ GASPS ]

29:21.931 --> 29:24.723
OH, MON DIEU! NOLAN!

29:24.723 --> 29:26.265
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

29:26.265 --> 29:27.436
[ BLADE SWOOSHES ]
 [ BOTH GRUNT ]

29:27.436 --> 29:28.597
[ GROANS ]
 [ KNIFE CLATTERS ]

29:28.597 --> 29:30.059
IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

29:30.059 --> 29:32.982
I'LL TAKE A KNIFE TO THE HAND
OVER 70,000 VOLTS ANY DAY.

29:32.982 --> 29:34.653
HERE. CHECK MY FRONT
JACKET POCKET.

29:34.653 --> 29:36.816
WHAT'S THIS?

29:36.816 --> 29:39.658
[ GROANS ] IT'S
HER CAYMAN ACCOUNT INFO.

29:39.658 --> 29:41.610
IT'S TIED TO RECORDS
OF EVERY FATAL ACCIDENT

29:41.610 --> 29:43.032
SHE'S EVER STAGED.

29:43.032 --> 29:45.494
DON'T WORRY. I REMOVED
THE CONNECTION TO YOU.

29:45.494 --> 29:47.206
I ALREADY CALLED THE POLICE.

29:47.206 --> 29:49.999
THEY'LL BE HERE
IN FIVE MINUTES.

29:49.999 --> 29:51.710
MARGAUX, YOU SHOULD GO.

29:51.710 --> 29:53.042
NO, I'M STAYING.

29:54.623 --> 29:58.127
I STARTED THIS TO GET JUSTICE
FOR DANIEL.

29:59.508 --> 30:02.922
HE ONCE TOLD ME NOT TO ABANDON
MY SOUL LIKE HE HAD.

30:04.093 --> 30:06.685
HE REDEEMED HIS
BY SAVING A LIFE.

30:06.685 --> 30:09.058
I NEED TO HONOR HIM
AND REDEEM MINE.

30:09.058 --> 30:10.309
WAIT.

30:10.309 --> 30:12.021
SO YOU'RE JUST GONNA
GIVE YOURSELF UP?

30:15.274 --> 30:20.029
IF IT'S OUR DECISIONS
THAT DEFINE WHO WE ARE,

30:20.029 --> 30:21.820
THEN THIS IS WHO I AM.

30:24.033 --> 30:26.575
BEFORE YOU FIRE,
PLEASE KNOW

30:26.575 --> 30:28.657
THAT LIKE
YOUR TELEVISED ASSASSINATION,

30:28.657 --> 30:32.211
YOUR REAL ONE WILL BE THERE
FOR ALL THE WORLD TO SEE.

30:32.211 --> 30:34.663
I INSTALLED THESE CAMERAS

30:34.663 --> 30:36.215
WHEN I HEARD
THAT YOU HAD ESCAPED,

30:36.215 --> 30:38.417
BECAUSE I KNEW THAT YOU WOULD
FIND YOUR WAY HERE.

30:38.417 --> 30:42.131
SO YOU'LL BE GOING AWAY FOR GOOD
ONCE YOU PULL THAT TRIGGER.

30:42.131 --> 30:45.014
YOU NEVER REALLY HAVE BEEN
ABLE TO, HAVE YOU?

30:45.014 --> 30:47.636
OH, FOR ONCE, YOU'RE RIGHT
ABOUT SOMETHING, VICTORIA.

30:47.636 --> 30:51.140
UNLIKE YOU,
I'VE NEVER KILLED ANYBODY.

30:51.140 --> 30:54.273
I BELIEVE THAT THE PEOPLE
WHO HURT MY FAMILY

30:54.273 --> 30:56.025
DESERVE TO LIVE IN AGONY,

30:56.025 --> 30:58.107
NOT PAY WITH THEIR LIVES.

30:58.107 --> 31:00.980
BUT YOU...

31:00.980 --> 31:04.033
YOU ARE THE ONE EXCEPTION.

31:04.033 --> 31:05.744
FOR YOU,

31:05.744 --> 31:09.368
DEATH IS
MY ONLY TRUE REVENGE.

31:14.123 --> 31:17.166
I DIED LONG BEFORE
YOU WERE BORN.

31:18.627 --> 31:21.050
THIS...

31:21.050 --> 31:23.092
IS JUST A FORMALITY.

31:27.096 --> 31:28.677
ARE YOU READY NOW?

31:28.677 --> 31:32.271
MORE THAN YOU KNOW.

31:32.271 --> 31:35.564
GOODBYE, VICTORIA.

31:35.564 --> 31:37.977
[ GUNSHOT ]
 [ GASPS ]

31:45.734 --> 31:48.737
DAD! WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU
DOING?! SHE WAS MINE!

31:48.737 --> 31:50.489
SAVING YOUR SOUL.

31:50.489 --> 31:52.701
YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHAT
CROSSING THAT LINE MEANS.

31:52.701 --> 31:53.912
[ Whispers ] OH, GOD.

31:53.912 --> 31:56.035
NO MATTER HOW JUSTIFIED.
IT'S OVER.

31:56.035 --> 31:57.997
NO.

31:59.798 --> 32:01.420
[ GUN THUDS ]

32:01.420 --> 32:02.711
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

32:02.711 --> 32:06.005
YOU DEVOTED YOUR LIFE
TO SAVING ME. IT'S MY TURN.

32:06.005 --> 32:07.466
I'M NOT GONNA LOSE YOU AGAIN.

32:07.466 --> 32:08.637
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
 I LOVE YOU, AMANDA.

32:08.637 --> 32:10.809
AND I LOVE YOU, TOO,

32:10.809 --> 32:12.011
WHICH IS WHY --
 [ GUNSHOT ]

32:12.011 --> 32:13.682
UHH!
 AAH!

32:13.682 --> 32:15.554
David: NO! NO!
 [ GUN THUDS ]

32:15.554 --> 32:18.267
[ GROANS ]
 NO.

32:21.560 --> 32:23.272
AMANDA, HOLD ON.

32:23.272 --> 32:24.563
COME ON, BABY.

32:24.563 --> 32:26.025
[ GRUNTS ]

32:26.025 --> 32:28.027
AMANDA.

32:42.251 --> 32:44.543
[ DAVID SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

32:51.090 --> 32:52.851
READY TO GO?

32:52.851 --> 32:54.263
[ BREATHES UNEVENLY ]

32:54.263 --> 32:57.186
THAT'S MY JOB, TO KEEP YOU
ON SCHEDULE TODAY.

32:58.187 --> 33:00.189
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]
I APPRECIATE IT.

33:03.062 --> 33:04.653
I'LL JUST BE A MINUTE.

33:26.085 --> 33:29.968
ISN'T IT BEAUTIFUL?

33:29.968 --> 33:32.261
I NEVER THOUGHT THAT...

33:32.261 --> 33:34.473
I WOULD GET
TO SIT HERE AGAIN.

33:34.473 --> 33:39.058
I'M GLAD THE JUDGE AGREED TO
GRANT YOU COMPASSIONATE RELEASE.

33:39.058 --> 33:40.519
[ Whispers ]
YOU DESERVE THIS.

33:40.519 --> 33:43.021
THIS, UH...

33:43.021 --> 33:45.354
CHANCE TO...

33:45.354 --> 33:46.905
GET TO KNOW YOU,

33:46.905 --> 33:48.647
SEE, UH,

33:48.647 --> 33:51.200
THE AMAZING WOMAN
THAT YOU'VE BECOME,

33:51.200 --> 33:56.034
HAS MADE ME FEEL
LIKE MY...

33:56.034 --> 33:59.037
MY LIFE IS COMPLETE.

33:59.037 --> 34:02.000
I CAN DIE A HAPPY MAN.

34:02.000 --> 34:04.923
[ Whispers ] OH, GOD.

34:04.923 --> 34:06.125
I'M GONNA MISS YOU SO MUCH.

34:06.125 --> 34:10.219
[ CRYING ]

34:10.219 --> 34:14.092
WHENEVER YOU...
 [ SNIFFLES ]

34:14.092 --> 34:16.675
MISS ME...
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:16.675 --> 34:19.598
GO TO THAT POST.

34:19.598 --> 34:23.021
GO ON. GO.

34:25.184 --> 34:27.896
REMEMBER HOW MUCH
I LOVE YOU.

34:27.896 --> 34:31.069
INFINITY...

34:31.069 --> 34:32.110
TIMES...

34:32.110 --> 34:33.992
[ Whispers ] INFINITY.

34:45.083 --> 34:47.505
DAD?

34:47.505 --> 34:50.007
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

34:50.007 --> 34:51.380
DAD?

34:58.557 --> 35:01.099
Amanda: UPON EMBARKING
ON A PATH OF REVENGE,

35:01.099 --> 35:04.983
CONFUCIUS WARNS
THAT ONE SHOULD DIG TWO GRAVES.

35:04.983 --> 35:07.936
[ CRYING ]

35:07.936 --> 35:10.359
CONFUCIUS WAS RIGHT.

35:10.359 --> 35:13.732
THE SECOND OF THE TWO GRAVES
WAS MEANT FOR ME.

35:13.732 --> 35:17.696
I WAS ONLY SAVED
BY MY FATHER'S INFINITE LOVE.

35:26.375 --> 35:31.049
I KNOW NOW THAT REVENGE BRINGS
ONLY DARKNESS.

35:31.049 --> 35:33.882
I COULDN'T SEE THE LIGHT UNTIL
I CONSIDERED MY FATHER'S ADVICE

35:33.882 --> 35:36.014
TO TRY AND FORGIVE.

35:37.806 --> 35:40.719
IT'S NOT EASY,

35:40.719 --> 35:43.602
BUT MY FATHER ONCE SAID THAT
NOTHING WORTH DOING EVER IS.

35:43.602 --> 35:47.226
WELL, WITH ONE EXCEPTION.

35:49.898 --> 35:51.190
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

35:51.190 --> 35:52.821
COME IN!

35:52.821 --> 35:55.904
[ DOOR OPENS ]

35:55.904 --> 35:59.117
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
IT'S ALMOST TIME.

35:59.117 --> 36:00.579
ANYTHING I CAN DO?

36:00.579 --> 36:02.831
UH, YEAH. CAN YOU HELP ME
WITH THIS?

36:08.497 --> 36:10.499
YOU KNOW, I WAS, UH...

36:10.499 --> 36:13.252
I WAS THINKING ABOUT THAT
FIRST NIGHT AT THE BEACH HOUSE.

36:13.252 --> 36:14.843
CALLED YOU OUT.

36:14.843 --> 36:18.797
YES. I BELIEVE I THREATENED
TO CRUSH YOUR WINDPIPE.

36:18.797 --> 36:20.178
GOOD TIMES.
 [ LAUGHS ]

36:20.178 --> 36:22.851
OH, THAT NIGHT, I...

36:22.851 --> 36:24.603
I OFFERED TO HELP YOU, TOO,

36:24.603 --> 36:26.895
AND YOU SAID I WASN'T
A PART OF THIS.

36:26.895 --> 36:29.398
CLEARLY, I WAS WRONG.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

36:29.398 --> 36:31.730
MM. BACK THEN,

36:31.730 --> 36:33.272
I WASN'T REALLY
PART OF ANYTHING.

36:33.272 --> 36:36.655
JUST...THE AWKWARD BILLIONAIRE.

36:36.655 --> 36:40.739
NO FRIENDS, NO LIFE.
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

36:40.739 --> 36:44.082
THE TIME
THAT WE SPENT TOGETHER...

36:44.082 --> 36:45.203
GAVE ME PURPOSE.

36:45.203 --> 36:46.415
[ Whispers ] I WAS GOOD AT IT.

36:46.415 --> 36:47.956
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

36:47.956 --> 36:49.998
NOW THAT IT'S OVER,
I JUST...

36:49.998 --> 36:51.790
I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S NEXT.

36:51.790 --> 36:55.003
NOLAN.
 AMS.

36:55.003 --> 36:57.045
I'M SERIOUS.

36:57.045 --> 36:59.718
IS THERE LIFE AFTER REVENGE
FOR NOLAN ROSS?

36:59.718 --> 37:03.262
OF COURSE THERE IS.

37:03.262 --> 37:07.306
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
YOU WILL FIND NEW PURPOSE.

37:07.306 --> 37:09.187
[ Whispers ] TRUST ME.

37:09.187 --> 37:11.189
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:11.189 --> 37:13.061
LET'S GET YOU DRESSED.

37:13.061 --> 37:15.944
I THINK YOU'VE MADE JACK WAIT
LONG ENOUGH. DON'T YOU?

37:15.944 --> 37:18.026
VERY FUNNY. [ CHUCKLES ]

37:18.026 --> 37:21.029
[ ANGUS & JULIA STONE'S
"FOR YOU" PLAYING ]

37:24.323 --> 37:29.207
♪ IF I TALK REAL SLOWLY ♪

37:31.370 --> 37:35.043
♪ IF I TRY REAL HARD ♪

37:37.796 --> 37:42.010
♪ TO MAKE MY POINT, DEAR ♪

37:44.092 --> 37:47.686
♪ THAT YOU HAVE MY HEART ♪

37:49.888 --> 37:53.482
♪ HERE I GO ♪

37:55.604 --> 38:00.359
♪ I'LL TELL YOU WHAT
YOU ALREADY KNOW ♪

38:02.030 --> 38:06.575
♪ HERE I GO ♪

38:07.956 --> 38:13.912
♪ I'LL TELL YOU WHAT
YOU ALREADY KNOW ♪

38:13.912 --> 38:19.127
♪ IF YOU LOVE ME ♪

38:19.127 --> 38:22.220
♪ WITH ALL OF YOUR HEART ♪
 [ CLINKING ]

38:22.220 --> 38:23.722
ON BEHALF OF AMANDA AND MYSELF,

38:23.722 --> 38:26.094
I'D LIKE TO TAKE A MOMENT
TO REMEMBER

38:26.094 --> 38:28.767
THE PEOPLE WE LOVE
WHO COULDN'T BE WITH US TODAY --

38:28.767 --> 38:30.769
MY BROTHER DECLAN,

38:30.769 --> 38:32.521
WHO ALWAYS ENCOURAGED ME

38:32.521 --> 38:35.934
TO BE THE BEST MAN
THAT I COULD BE...

38:35.934 --> 38:37.105
EMILY THORNE,

38:37.105 --> 38:40.779
TO WHOM WE BOTH OWE OUR LIVES
AND WHO BROUGHT MY --

38:40.779 --> 38:43.652
MY BEAUTIFUL SON CARL
INTO THIS WORLD.

38:45.654 --> 38:47.406
AND MY FATHER CARL SENIOR,

38:47.406 --> 38:50.078
AND OUR FRIENDS AIDEN AND BEN.

38:50.078 --> 38:52.160
AND FINALLY...

38:52.160 --> 38:54.292
DAVID,

38:54.292 --> 38:55.954
WHO WE LOST EARLIER THIS YEAR.

38:55.954 --> 38:58.917
[ INHALES SHARPLY ] WE MISS YOU
ALL MORE THAN WORDS CAN SAY.

38:58.917 --> 39:00.379
TO DAVID.
 Woman: HEAR, HEAR.

39:00.379 --> 39:02.421
[ GUESTS MURMURING ]

39:02.421 --> 39:04.463
YOU KNOW,
IT WAS DAVID WHO BROUGHT

39:04.463 --> 39:06.054
AMANDA AND I TOGETHER
AS KIDS,

39:06.054 --> 39:08.226
AND...

39:08.226 --> 39:09.678
REUNITED US YEARS LATER

39:09.678 --> 39:11.640
WITH THE PASSION THAT
HE INSTILLED IN HIS DAUGHTER.

39:11.640 --> 39:15.023
AND IT'S HIS LEGACY NOW...
 [ TAPS TABLETOP ]

39:15.023 --> 39:16.144
THAT SETS US OFF
ON OUR FIRST JOURNEY

39:16.144 --> 39:17.476
AS HUSBAND AND WIFE.

39:17.476 --> 39:19.978
AMANDA AND I WILL BE LEAVING
ON THE BOAT

39:19.978 --> 39:22.070
THAT HE PAINSTAKINGLY RESTORED
FOR US.

39:22.070 --> 39:24.032
AND... [ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

39:24.032 --> 39:25.784
WELL, WE'RE JUST LUCKY
TO HAVE YOU ALL HERE WITH US

39:25.784 --> 39:27.285
TO -- TO SEE US OFF. SO...

39:27.285 --> 39:29.788
THANK YOU.
 [ APPLAUSE ]

39:29.788 --> 39:31.249
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

39:31.249 --> 39:33.121
NOW THAT I HAVE
ALL OF YOUR ATTENTION,

39:33.121 --> 39:34.993
THERE'S A LITTLE SOMETHING

39:34.993 --> 39:37.416
THAT I WANTED TO GIVE
MY NEW HUSBAND.

39:37.416 --> 39:39.377
NOLAN?

39:39.377 --> 39:41.169
Guests: AW!

39:41.169 --> 39:42.591
[ LAUGHING ]

39:42.591 --> 39:44.803
I CONSIDER MYSELF LUCKY.

39:44.803 --> 39:48.096
MOST MORALITY TALES DON'T HAVE
A HAPPY ENDING.

39:48.096 --> 39:49.508
FOR SOME REASON,

39:49.508 --> 39:52.310
KARMA SAW FIT TO SPARE ME,

39:52.310 --> 39:56.104
BUT NOT WITHOUT LEAVING
DEEPLY ETCHED WOUNDS.

39:56.104 --> 39:59.778
[ MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY ]

39:59.778 --> 40:03.071
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

40:03.071 --> 40:04.573
IS SHE GOING TO MAKE IT?

40:04.573 --> 40:06.695
TIME WILL TELL.

40:06.695 --> 40:09.117
WHAT SHE WENT THROUGH
WAS EXTREMELY TRAUMATIC,

40:09.117 --> 40:11.580
BUT THE SURGERY WAS A SUCCESS.

40:11.580 --> 40:15.033
YOUR SISTER OWES YOU
HER LIFE.

40:15.033 --> 40:18.497
BUT SHE CAN NEVER KNOW HOW.

40:18.497 --> 40:21.630
OR RATHER, WHO.

40:21.630 --> 40:22.921
AS YOU WISH.

40:22.921 --> 40:25.714
BUT IT'S EXTRAORDINARY
THAT THEY WERE A MATCH.

40:25.714 --> 40:28.306
AMANDA'S HEART WAS DAMAGED
BEYOND REPAIR.

40:28.306 --> 40:31.640
IF YOU HADN'T VOLUNTEERED
VICTORIA'S FOR TRANSPLANT...

40:31.640 --> 40:34.432
IT'S WHAT MOTHER
WOULD'VE WANTED.

40:43.482 --> 40:46.274
[ GASPS ]

40:46.274 --> 40:47.986
YOU HAD THAT DREAM AGAIN.

40:47.986 --> 40:49.277
OHH.

40:49.277 --> 40:51.369
[ SEABIRDS CALLING ]

40:51.369 --> 40:54.452
I JUST CAN'T GET IT
OUT OF MY HEAD.

40:54.452 --> 40:56.915
IT'S SO REAL. [ GROANS ]

40:56.915 --> 40:58.126
[ SIGHS ]

40:58.126 --> 41:00.789
WELL, IT'S NOT.

41:00.789 --> 41:02.130
T'S JUST A NIGHTMARE.

41:04.042 --> 41:07.796
[ SIGHS ] I'LL NEVER BE ABLE
TO PUT HER BEHIND ME, WILL I?

41:20.559 --> 41:22.480
I LOVE YOU, JACK PORTER.

41:24.863 --> 41:27.986
I LOVE YOU, AMANDA CLARKE.

41:27.986 --> 41:31.780
WHEN EVERYTHING YOU LOVE
HAS BEEN STOLEN FROM YOU,

41:31.780 --> 41:33.201
CONSIDER MY STORY

41:33.201 --> 41:35.824
AS YOU EMBARK ON
YOUR OWN JOURNEY OF REVENGE.

41:48.927 --> 41:50.508
EXCUSE ME, MR. ROSS?

41:50.508 --> 41:52.260
MM.

41:52.260 --> 41:54.052
AMANDA CLARKE SAID THAT
YOU COULD HELP ME.

41:54.052 --> 41:56.845
AND ALWAYS REMEMBER...

41:56.845 --> 41:58.226
THAT'S MY MOM.

41:59.848 --> 42:03.311
WHAT GOES AROUND, COMES AROUND.

42:04.482 --> 42:06.565
SHE'S INNOCENT.

42:12.450 --> 42:14.242
WELL PLAYED, AMS.

42:15.994 --> 42:18.116
WELL PLAYED.

42:18.116 --> 42:21.499
♪♪♪
